WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:05.520
Now again, as a publisher, I have some additional controls. And the most important thing is I'm a

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:12.320
publisher, how do I then share it with the people that need to see it? And that's going to be right

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:19.040
here under access controls. Now we have it set by default to specific users or groups. And if you

00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:24.959
look right underneath, you can define those users and groups right here. I'm currently the only one

00:00:24.959 --> 00:00:31.440
that can view this content. But let's say for example, I want to give Rachel access. Now we

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:36.160
would be the only two that can view this content. So really tight control over who you want to share

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:41.680
this application with, which is great, especially if you have any sensitive data. But we can be a

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:47.360
little less strict. So if you look at the middle option right here, all users login required. If I

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:53.119
select this, basically, as long as you can log into the Connect instance, you can view this content.

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:58.560
So here are positive is our demo environment, that's pretty much all positive employees,

00:00:58.560 --> 00:01:04.720
they can log into the Connect instance, they can view it. But we can be even less strict and select

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:11.440
anyone, no login required. And if I do that, basically this application, this dashboard we

00:01:11.440 --> 00:01:17.440
created when hosted on Connect is opened up to the world. So if anyone has this URL on the top

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:22.480
of the screen, you see right here, they can view this content. Now, if you look at this URL, you

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:27.599
can see it's not the prettiest URL to some random letters and numbers up here. We can change that

00:01:27.599 --> 00:01:33.199
we can give this a more customized URL. So I can come down here to content URL. And I can just say

00:01:33.199 --> 00:01:40.720
dash app and hit save. And now we have this customized URL at the bottom of my screen,

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:46.480
which we can then share with the world and anyone can view this content.

